OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, fine
OL,6,Fevening, though rather windy. A clear
OL,7,Fnight will follow, and becoming chilly
OL,8,Fin sheltered spots. Winds abating a
OL,9,Flittle, though a brisk breeze
OL,10,Fpersisting.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FFine, dry and sunny, though
OL,13,Frather windy once again, with the
OL,14,Fstrongest winds near coasts and across
OL,15,Fhills. Warm inland but cooler along
OL,16,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
